                    </div>
                    <span>This book has been very helpful in my struggle to break out of beginning sewing.  It helps the reader construct garments on a much more professional level.  And it helps you to alter existing patterns to create your own design ideas as well as make your own patterns from scratch.  I don't know if this would be really useful for someone who is very advanced in his or her sewing skills, but for someone like me it's a huge eye opener and a great introduction to pattern drafting.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Expected alot more than received</div>
